        "fullContent": "<p>[X] I affirm the direction set out in the mandate, will help translate it into thoroughly reasoned strategies for my domain, and will maintain an exclusive and energetic focus on the mission-critical tasks necessary for its implementation, from today until my last day at the EF.</p>\n<hr/>\n<blockquote>\n<b>Aerugo (@aerugoettinea)</b>\n<p>\n<p>[X] I affirm the direction set out in the mandate, will help translate it into thoroughly reasoned strategies for my domain, and will maintain an exclusive and energetic focus on the mission-critical tasks necessary for its implementation, from today until my last day at the EF.</p>\n<img src=\"https://nitter.net/pic/media%2FHD3k3n3XQAAw8wP.jpg\" style=\"max-width:250px;\" />\n\n\n</p>\n<footer>\n— <cite><a href=\"https://nitter.net/aerugoettinea/status/2035034378904969459#m\">https://nitter.net/aerugoettinea/status/2035034378904969459#m</a>\n</footer>\n</blockquote>",
