      {
        "id": "2034587465382514773",
        "title": "RT by @VitalikButerin: Alice swaps privately on L1\n\ntldr: Privacy protocol users today depend on broadcasters that can see, frontrun, and censor their transactions. In this thread we show how four future protocol upgrades can remove this dependency step by step. Native AA (EIP-8141) and 2D nonces let users self-submit with no off-chain infrastructure. Encrypted frame transactions hide swap parameters until after block ordering is committed. FOCIL guarantees inclusion as long as one honest includer can see the transaction pending in the public mempool.\n\n👇🧵",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/soispoke/status/2034587465382514773#m",
        "content": "Alice swaps privately on L1\n\ntldr: Privacy protocol users today depend on broadcasters that can see, frontrun, and censor their transactions. In this thread we show how four future protocol upgrades can remove this dependency step by step. Native AA (EIP-8141) and 2D nonces let users self-submit with no off-chain infrastructure. Encrypted frame transactions hide swap parameters until after block ordering is committed. FOCIL guarantees inclusion as long as one honest includer can see the transaction pending in the public mempool.\n\n👇🧵",
        "fullContent": "<p>Alice swaps privately on L1<br>\n<br>\ntldr: Privacy protocol users today depend on broadcasters that can see, frontrun, and censor their transactions. In this thread we show how four future protocol upgrades can remove this dependency step by step. Native AA (EIP-8141) and 2D nonces let users self-submit with no off-chain infrastructure. Encrypted frame transactions hide swap parameters until after block ordering is committed. FOCIL guarantees inclusion as long as one honest includer can see the transaction pending in the public mempool.<br>\n<br>\n👇🧵</p>\n<img src=\"https://nitter.net/pic/media%2FHDxNnDFXgAABYPu.jpg\" style=\"max-width:250px;\" />",
        "author": "@soispoke",
        "date": "2026-03-19T11:07:07.000Z",
        "image": "https://nitter.net/pic/media%2FHDxNnDFXgAABYPu.jpg"
      },
      {
        "id": "2034068688651907530",
        "title": "Open-source vaccines, so the whole world can participate in manufacturing them and in better analyzing and understanding their medical properties.\n\nFunded by Balvi.\n\nThe full-stack d/acc roadmap is shipping.\n\nhttps://firefly.social/post/x/2034007336768200832",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/VitalikButerin/status/2034068688651907530#m",
        "content": "Open-source vaccines, so the whole world can participate in manufacturing them and in better analyzing and understanding their medical properties.\nfirefly.social/post/x/203400…",
        "fullContent": "<p>Open-source vaccines, so the whole world can participate in manufacturing them and in better analyzing and understanding their medical properties.<br>\n<br>\nFunded by Balvi.<br>\n<br>\nThe full-stack d/acc roadmap is shipping.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://firefly.social/post/x/2034007336768200832\">firefly.social/post/x/203400…</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://nitter.net/pic/card_img%2F2034068696025489409%2Fh6tqFe6v%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D800x419\" style=\"max-width:250px;\" />",
