      {
        "id": "2034067492595790149",
        "title": "An excellent post explaining the importance of Ethereum having a dynamically available consensus, that both provides economic finality and ensures chain progress even under conditions where economic finality is impossible.\n\nhttps://firefly.social/post/x/2033908939088400655",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/VitalikButerin/status/2034067492595790149#m",
        "content": "An excellent post explaining the importance of Ethereum having a dynamically available consensus, that both provides economic finality and ensures chain progress even under conditions where economic finality is impossible.\nfirefly.social/post/x/203390…",
        "fullContent": "<p>An excellent post explaining the importance of Ethereum having a dynamically available consensus, that both provides economic finality and ensures chain progress even under conditions where economic finality is impossible.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://firefly.social/post/x/2033908939088400655\">firefly.social/post/x/203390…</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://nitter.net/pic/card_img%2F2034484164611960832%2FrI2CYNX3%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D800x419\" style=\"max-width:250px;\" />",
