      {
        "id": "2034067549160116247",
        "title": "R to @VitalikButerin: Once @leanethereum is fully deployed, Ethereum will be the only major chain that simultaneously has (i) theoretically optimal security properties under synchrony [requires 51% of online validators honest], and (ii) strong economic finality under asynchrony. Most \"semi-centralized fast chains\" pick (ii) only, PoW chains pick (i) only, Ethereum gets both.",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/VitalikButerin/status/2034067549160116247#m",
        "content": "Once @leanethereum is fully deployed, Ethereum will be the only major chain that simultaneously has (i) theoretically optimal security properties under synchrony [requires 51% of online validators honest], and (ii) strong economic finality under asynchrony. Most \"semi-centralized fast chains\" pick (ii) only, PoW chains pick (i) only, Ethereum gets both.",
        "fullContent": "<p>Once <a href=\"https://nitter.net/leanethereum\" title=\"lean Ethereum\">@leanethereum</a> is fully deployed, Ethereum will be the only major chain that simultaneously has (i) theoretically optimal security properties under synchrony [requires 51% of online validators honest], and (ii) strong economic finality under asynchrony. Most \"semi-centralized fast chains\" pick (ii) only, PoW chains pick (i) only, Ethereum gets both.</p>",
        "author": "@VitalikButerin",
        "date": "2026-03-18T00:41:09.000Z",
        "image": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2034066521937326556",
        "title": "A new fast confirmation rule mechanism lets you get a hard guarantee that Ethereum will not revert after one slot (12 seconds)\n\nSecurity assumptions are (i) supermajority honest, (ii) network latency under ~3s. So one step below economic finality, but very strong for many use cases.\n\nhttps://firefly.social/post/x/2033852383290102109",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/VitalikButerin/status/2034066521937326556#m",
        "content": "A new fast confirmation rule mechanism lets you get a hard guarantee that Ethereum will not revert after one slot (12 seconds)\nfirefly.social/post/x/203385…",
        "fullContent": "<p>A new fast confirmation rule mechanism lets you get a hard guarantee that Ethereum will not revert after one slot (12 seconds)<br>\n<br>\nSecurity assumptions are (i) supermajority honest, (ii) network latency under ~3s. So one step below economic finality, but very strong for many use cases.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://firefly.social/post/x/2033852383290102109\">firefly.social/post/x/203385…</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://nitter.net/pic/card_img%2F2034066528291753984%2F7XnpljAt%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D800x419\" style=\"max-width:250px;\" />",
        "author": "@VitalikButerin",
        "date": "2026-03-18T00:37:04.000Z",
        "image": "https://nitter.net/pic/card_img%2F2034066528291753984%2F7XnpljAt%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D800x419"
      },
      {
        "id": "2033016361866375336",
        "title": "RT by @VitalikButerin: we do this with http://client.buidlguidl.com ser",
        "link": "https://nitter.net/austingriffith/status/2033016361866375336#m",
        "content": "we do this with client.buidlguidl.com ser",
